description: Node All-Star is a pan-entertainment eco-community based on the EOS.IO blockchain platform. It adopts the Proof of Opinion to form a token reward and feedback to the community members who contributed to the Node All-Star community ecology and allows them to exchange customized services, merchandise, etc. with their awards in the ecosystem. Meanwhile, a credible star business value measurement system has been precipitated to promote more benign development of the entertainment industry.
name: Node All-Star
